node.text:
Prepare yourselves... @whatsthomaseating and I challenged each other to a blind taste test of the new @edys @dreyers Rocky Road Collection and honestly, I've never loved my job more!! Take a wild guess who has the better palate.... #ad

If you're down to get crazy and try all the insanely delish flavors, THIS IS YOUR MOMENT. Now through Wednesday, June 9, buy just one full-size flavor from the EDY'S or Dreyer’s recently launched and get the rest of the collection for free when you share a photo of your ice cream on Instagram. Details on how to enter are below! Which flavor would you try first?

🍦 Purchase one of the six Rocky Road Collection flavors at a national grocery retailer near you. Mocha Almond Avenue, Brownie Brick Road, Cookie Cobblestone, Chocolate Peanut Butter Park, Salted Caramel Pretzel Path and/or The Original Rocky Road
🍦 Share a photo of your purchase on Instagram via an in-feed post or Instagram story using the #NationalRockyRoadDay. Can’t make it to the store? No problem! Just comment on @edys or @dreyers promotion post using #NationalRockyRoadDay with one sentence about which flavor of the Rocky Road Collection you’re most excited to try and why.
🍦 Make sure you’re following @edys and @dreyers and tag the handles in your post. Don’t forget to set your profile to Public so they can see your entry!
🍦 EDY'S (Dreyer's) will direct message eligible entrants while supplies last with next steps on how to claim their free ice cream!
NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Limit to one entry per person. Open to legal residents of the 50 United States (D.C), 13 and older. Entries must be received by 11:59pm PDT on 6/9/21. For Official Rules, go to the link in the @edys @dreyers bio.

node.text: Boring pasta salads are a thing of the past! Get ready for this jammy, delish, mayo free tomato confit pasta salad! It’s good warm, at room temp or cold! node.text: One of my fav summer dishes is happening tonight: Summer Clams with a White Wine Sauce! The full recipe is on WGC (linked in my profile) and I used my go-to @allclad D5 Stainless Cookware Set to make this perfect al-fresco meal. The D5 Stainless Cookware Collection is one of my absolute favs – and it’s what you see on IG live week after week. The collection is made using a patented 5-ply construction of alternating layers of stainless steel and aluminum, meaning that you’ll have an evenly heated cooking surface every time – no hot spots! As you know, we’re celebrating All-Clad’s 50th anniversary ALL YEAR LONG, and we’re giving away a D5 Stainless 7pc Set during this month’s WGC Cooking Club! All-Clad is also offering a limited-time discount for WGC followers – code available in my IG stories. These beauties last forever, so if you’re in the market for some new cookware, here’s your chance! https://whatsgabycooking.com/steamed-clams-with-garlic-and-chives/

node.text:
National Ice Cream Day is right around the corner!! Best day of the summer (minus my birthday) if you ask me!! #ad Teamed up with @edys to bring you some inspiration to celebrate the big day and make sure you’re hooked up with some free ice cream! EDY’S (Dreyer’s) latest Rocky Road Collection has something for everyone, and I’m setting out to help you find your PERFECT MATCH from the collection (plus, their new flavors make the best ice cream sandwiches 😉). There's a handy dandy little quiz to find your perfect match if you swipe left! Just follow the prompts and let me know what flavor you get in the comments. Thomas is without a doubt on the Peanut Butter Park train and I'm a toss-up between Brownie Brick Road and Cookie Cobblestone. Once you have your free ice cream, just whip up some cookies, sandwich that ice cream flavor in between and you're in business for the tastiest day of the year!

🍦 Following the prompts on the quiz, comment down below in one sentence which flavor of the Rocky Road Collection you matched with, and why you’re excited to try it!

🍦 Make sure you’re following @edys or @dreyers and tag the handle in your comment. Don’t forget to use #NationalIceCreamDay2021.

🍦 EDY’S (Dreyer’s) will direct message eligible entrants while supplies last with next steps on how to claim their free ice cream – now isn’t that sweet!

NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Limit to one entry per person. Open to legal residents of the 50 United States (D.C), 13 or older. Entries must be received by 11:59pm PDT on July 16, 2021. For Official Rules, go to the link in @edys or @dreyers bio.
